spells.description:
Use: Take what is rightfully yours, gorging on your target's essence to deal 3.6 million Shadow damage and healing you for 546,044 over 2 sec. Damage and healing increased based on the target's missing health.

Cooldown reduced by 60 sec if this effect kills the target. (2 Min Cooldown)
Equip: Your attacks have a chance to harmonize with the shard, granting you 15,260 Agility for 15 sec.
Equip: Damaging a target has a low chance to call upon the power of the Blessed Weapon Grip, granting you 10 stacks that increase your highest secondary stat by 185. These stacks fade over 30 sec.
